# Ignore large and binary data files to avoid tracking in Git
# Add patterns for common data file types
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.gz
*.tif
*.tiff
*.nc
*.hdf
*.csv
*.json
*.xml
*.shp
*.dbf
*.prj
*.shx
# For large files, consider using Git LFS if needed
# Install Git LFS and track large files with: git lfs track "*.tif" etc.